title: Import of creamery butter in Canada 2020
summary: The graph illustrates the Import of creamery in Canada the year 2020 .
The Import is very low in the first third of the year , before it rises sharply until October , reaching a maximum of 20000 Tonnes .
Then the Import reduced again for the remaining months of the year .
gold: A chart about Canada 's creamery butter imports in 2020 , measured in tonnes . It increases before dropping dramatically and finally rebounds to new highs .
